ance Corp.andM;Bankers Trust Co. is the nation's seventh largest bank.andP;  Its mer- chantbanking strategy, which combines commercial and investment banking, hashelped make Bankers Trust one of the most profitable financial services overthe last 10 years.andM;Key Executives: Frank Paccione, vp, Communications Engineering, Bankers TrustCo.andM;EDGE NOTE: HOW DID NORTHERN GET THE BANKERS TRUST CONTRACT? For one thing,ATandamp;T's introduction of their &quot;Universal Credit Card,&quot; a competitive offeringto Bankers Trust's own card didn't hurt.andP;  For another, a newly organizedNorthern Telecom, Network Integration division, was obviously at work,pitching the benefits of 'alternate vendor' support.andM;For more on the new Northern Telecom, Network Integration Divi- sion, seenext story.andO;</TEXT></DOC>